    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Used car in fair overall condition. It starts, runs, and drives, and it should be fine for basic daily transportation, but it clearly shows age and use. Expect visible cosmetic wear inside and out, including scratches, scuffs, and general signs of use, and buyers should not expect a like-new vehicle. A practical option for someone looking for dependable transportation at a fair price, with normal upkeep likely to come with an older used car.",
