    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for a value-focused buyer, commuter, or project-minded owner. It presents as an honest, affordable option with solid everyday potential and plenty of upside for someone looking to secure transportation without stretching the budget. Priced to sell and offering clear value in its segment, this is a straightforward purchase for anyone seeking low-cost entry into ownership.",
