    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect and I\u2019d rather be upfront about that, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants an affordable runaround, a first project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind, and for the money it offers a lot of potential. If you\u2019re after something honest, budget-friendly, and worth a look, send me a message \u2014 happy to chat.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or inexpensive daily with good bones. This car shows its age cosmetically and will need some TLC, but it starts, runs, and has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it appealing for someone who likes to wrench. Engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels usable around town. A great candidate for a commuter, backup vehicle, or weekend restore without a huge upfront cost. Priced to move and worth a look if you want something affordable with potential.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Honest poor-condition ride with plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a true diamond-in-the-rough for someone who sees potential where others see a weekend project. It carries itself with a scrappy, seasoned presence and offers a chance to own an affordable ride with plenty of story left to tell. Perfect for a hands-on buyer, a budget commuter experiment, or someone looking for a platform to revive and make their own. If you appreciate grit, possibility, and the satisfaction of bringing something back to life, this one is calling your name.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
