      "description": "Reliable transportation at a smart price. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically, but it offers solid value for someone seeking an affordable daily driver, backup car, or practical project. A straightforward opportunity to own a usable vehicle without overpaying, presented honestly and priced to move.",
