    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, moves, and offers a great opportunity for someone handy, in need of cheap transport, or after a solid little project. It\u2019s being sold honestly as a well-used vehicle, and the price reflects that, but there\u2019s still real value here for anyone who sees the potential. If you want something affordable without the big price tag, this could be well worth a look.",
